'''Briccriu'''

# (''Irish mythology'') In the [[Ulster Cycle]] of [[Irish]] [[mythology]]: a warrior, poet, and troublemaker who once held a lavish feast for [[Conchobar mac Nessa]] and the heroes of [[Ulster]] in his house at [[Dún Rudraige]].